parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition interlock system can cause the vehicle to roll unattended, leading to potential accidents or injuries, especially if children are left unattended in the vehicle.
symptoms: The ignition key can be removed from the steering column when the gear shift is in any position
the gear shift can be moved from park to any other position without the key inserted
the vehicle can roll backwards or move unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, slip out of gear, or become stuck in gear, leading to potential accidents or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of gear
the vehicle breaks down frequently
the transmission needs to be rebuilt or replaced multiple times.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Stalling and Failure to Restart
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling and failing to restart can cause accidents, injuries, or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs in heavy traffic or hazardous locations.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops running while in motion
the vehicle will not start again
the vehicle stalls and fails to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Battery failure can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to inconvenience, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the battery is dead or drained.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Computer failure can cause the vehicle to malfunction, stall, or fail to start, leading to accidents, injuries, or inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the vehicle's engine or transmission malfunctions
error codes or warning lights appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Pulse generator failure can cause the vehicle to malfunction, stall, or fail to start, leading to accidents, injuries, or inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or fails to start
the vehicle's engine or transmission malfunctions
error codes or warning lights appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the safety belt system can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the belt may not properly restrain the occupant.
symptoms: The shoulder belt breaks
the motor belt fails
the safety belt gets stuck in the middle position of the mechanism
the safety belt does not retract or function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power window system can cause inconvenience, difficulty in operating the windows, and potentially lead to safety issues if the driver is unable to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: Multiple power windows are inoperative
only one window is working
unable to open or close windows from the inside or outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock system can cause security concerns, as the driver may be unable to lock the doors, and potentially lead to safety issues if the doors are not securely closed.
symptoms: Unable to lock the doors with the key
only one door can be opened from the outside
inconsistent door lock functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heater control knob can cause inconvenience and discomfort for the driver and passengers, as they may be unable to adjust the heating system.
symptoms: Heater control knob falls off
unable to adjust the heating system.
